entries.femaleVariant: Ugh, it reeks again. I'm tellin' ya, one fine day this stench's gonna burn a hole clean through our lungs.
Mary says it is leak from Petrochem.
It was. Neighbor's kids was playin' by this nasty thing near two hours till someone caught on.
Littlest one inhaled so much of it she started foamin' at the mouth. Saw it myself.
Terrible parents... If you make kids, you must watch them too!
